ISLAMABAD, Jul 22 (APP):President Asif Ali Zardari on Monday commended the security forces for thwarting terrorists’ infiltration attempt along the Pak-Afghan border in Dir district.
According to a President House statement, the President acknowledged the swift response of Pakistani forces to terrorists on the Pak-Afghan border, emphasizing the nation’s unity with the security forces in ensuring national defense, peace, and security.
